data.description: CHECK OUT THE NEW PRICE REDUCTION!!! This amazing home sits on over 5 acres with a pond. This home gives you much room to roam. This property comes with a workshop (30x60), detached garage (24x25) and a well house w/90ft well. The home is all electric and is equipped with a Generac Generator. No worries during storm season with the 4x8 safe room in the garage plus an in-ground storm shelter as well! Extras include 2 propane tanks, 1 two ton wench in the shop, chicken coop, caged dog kennel and fiber optic internet with up to 1 gigabit. HVAC installed in 2019. Large living area w/built ins and kitchen is wide open! Tons of cabinets and a pantry for lots of storage. All bedrooms are nice and spacious. Livestock is allowed and NO HOA!! Don't miss out on this wonderful opportunity to own such an amazing property and all it has to offer!
